# Market Insights Project Structure

## Repository Overview
This is a full-stack financial data analysis application with:
- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Python FastAPI
- **Data Processing**: Financial market data analysis and breadth metrics

## Directory Structure
- `app/` - FastAPI backend application
  - `main.py` - FastAPI app entry point
  - `routes/` - API route handlers
  - `config.py` - Configuration management
- `engine/` - Data processing engine
  - `providers/` - Data source providers
  - `jobs/` - Data processing jobs
  - `out/` - Processed data outputs (Parquet files)
- `frontend/` - React frontend application
  - `src/components/` - React components
  - `src/lib/` - Utility functions and API clients
- `data/` - Raw and processed data files
- `tests/` - Test files mirroring source structure
- `tools/` - Utility scripts for data processing

## Key Files
- [app/main.py](mdc:app/main.py) - FastAPI application entry point
- [frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/App.tsx) - React application root
- [config.yaml](mdc:config.yaml) - Application configuration
- [Makefile](mdc:Makefile) - Build and deployment commands
